This paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) category as it deals with the design of recommender systems. It could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories as it involves optimization and modeling techniques. Additionally, it could be categorized under Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) as recommender systems are often used in social networks. Finally, it could also be classified under Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) as it involves matrix completion techniques.
